trans-unit.source: Uses a mask to distinguish between proper and improper user input.
trans-unit.target: 使用掩码区分正确的和不正确的用户输入。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> class is an enhanced <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox> control that supports a declarative syntax for accepting or rejecting user input.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>类是一个增强型<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>支持的声明性语法用于接受或拒绝用户输入的控件。

trans-unit.source: Using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Mask%2A> property, you can specify the following input without writing any custom validation logic in your application:
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Mask%2A>属性，你可以指定以下输入而无需编写任何自定义验证逻辑应用程序中：

trans-unit.source: Required input characters.
trans-unit.target: 必需的输入的字符。

trans-unit.source: Optional input characters.
trans-unit.target: 可选的输入的字符。

trans-unit.source: The type of input expected at a given position in the mask; for example, a digit, or an alphabetic or alphanumeric character.
trans-unit.target: 需掩码; 中的给定位置的输入类型例如，一个数字或字母或字母数字字符。

trans-unit.source: Mask literals, or characters that should appear directly in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>; for example, the hyphens (-) in a phone number, or the currency symbol in a price.
trans-unit.target: 屏蔽文本，显示或字符应直接在<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>; 例如，在该电话号码或在价格的货币符号的连字符 （-）。

trans-unit.source: Special processing for input characters; for example, to convert alphabetic characters to uppercase.
trans-unit.target: 对输入字符; 特殊处理例如，若要转换为大写的字母字符。

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control is displayed at run time, it represents the mask as a series of prompt characters and optional literal characters.
trans-unit.target: 当<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>控件显示在运行时，它表示为一系列的提示字符和可选的原义字符的掩码。

trans-unit.source: Each editable mask position, representing a required or optional input, is shown with a single prompt character.
trans-unit.target: 表示的必需或可选的输入，每个可编辑掩码位置还会显示一个提示字符。

trans-unit.source: For example, the number sign (#) is often used as a placeholder for a numeric character input.
trans-unit.target: 例如，数字符号 （#） 通常用于以占位符形式的数字字符输入。

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PromptChar%2A> property to specify a custom prompt character.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PromptChar%2A>属性指定自定义的提示字符。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.HidePromptOnLeave%2A> property determines if the user sees the prompt characters when the control loses input focus.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.HidePromptOnLeave%2A>属性确定用户能否看到的提示字符当控件失去输入焦点。

trans-unit.source: As the user types input into the masked text box, valid input characters replace their respective prompt characters in a sequential fashion.
trans-unit.target: 如在掩蔽的文本框中输入的用户类型，有效的输入的字符将按顺序其各自的提示字符。

trans-unit.source: If the user types an invalid input character, no replacement occurs, but instead a beep is issued if the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.BeepOnError%2A> property is set to `true`, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: 如果用户键入无效的输入的字符，没有可以代替会发生，但如果改为发出播放提示音<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.BeepOnError%2A>属性设置为`true`，和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected>引发事件。

trans-unit.source: You can provide your own custom error logic by handing this event.
trans-unit.target: 你可以通过处理此事件来提供您自己自定义错误的逻辑。

trans-unit.source: When the current insertion point is at a literal character, the user has a number of options:
trans-unit.target: 原义字符在当前的插入点时，用户将具有多个选项：

trans-unit.source: If a character other than the prompt character is typed, the literal will automatically be skipped and the input character will be applied to the next editable position, represented by the next prompt character.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型提示字符以外的字符，文本将自动跳过，并输入的字符将应用到下一个可编辑位置表示下一步的提示字符。

trans-unit.source: If the prompt character is typed and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AllowPromptAsInput%2A> property is true, the input will overtype the prompt character and insertion point will be moved to the next position in the mask.
trans-unit.target: 如果提示字符为类型化和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AllowPromptAsInput%2A>属性为 true 时，输入将覆盖的提示字符和插入点将被移动到掩码中的下一个位置。

trans-unit.source: As is always the case, the arrow keys can be used to navigate to a previous or subsequent position.
trans-unit.target: 由于始终是这种情况，可以使用箭头键导航到上一或下一个位置。

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskFull%2A> property to verify whether or not the user has entered all of the required input.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskFull%2A>属性以验证是否用户是否输入了所有必需的输入。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> property will always retrieve the user's input formatted according to the mask and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>属性将始终检索按照掩码设置格式的用户的输入和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control actually defers all mask processing to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MaskedTextProvider?displayProperty=nameWithType> class specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>控件实际上将推迟到的所有掩码处理<xref:System.ComponentModel.MaskedTextProvider?displayProperty=nameWithType>指定类<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: This standard provider supports all Unicode characters except for surrogates and vertically combined characters; however, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AsciiOnly%2A> property can be used to restrict input to the characters sets a-z, A-Z, and 0-9.
trans-unit.target: 此标准的提供程序支持除外代理项的所有 Unicode 字符和垂直组合字符;但是，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AsciiOnly%2A>属性可以用于限制输入连接到字符集 a 到 z、 A 到 Z 和 0-9。

trans-unit.source: Masks do not necessarily guarantee that a user's input will represent a valid value for a given type; for example, -9 could be entered for an age in years.
trans-unit.target: 掩码并不一定能保证用户的输入将表示对于给定的类型; 有效的值例如，-9 无法输入的年龄的年数。

trans-unit.source: You can verify that a user's input represents a valid value by assigning an instance of that value's type to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 你可以验证用户的输入通过分配到的值的类型的实例表示有效的值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: You can detect whether the user removes focus from <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> when it contains an invalid value by monitoring for the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event.
trans-unit.target: 你可以检测用户是否删除焦点从<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>时监视包含无效值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>事件。

trans-unit.source: If type validation succeeds, the object representing the value will be available through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ReturnValue%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs> parameter.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型验证成功，表示的值的对象将通过<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ReturnValue%2A>属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs>参数。

trans-unit.source: As with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox> control, several common keyboard shortcuts do not work with <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>.
trans-unit.target: 与<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>控件，不能使用几个常见的键盘快捷方式<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>。

trans-unit.source: In particular, CTRL-R (right justify text), CTRL-L (left justify text), and CTRL-L (center text) have no effect.
trans-unit.target: 具体而言，CTRL-R （右对齐文本），CTRL-L （左对齐文本），并且 CTRL-L （center 文本） 产生任何影响。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the user can enter the prompt character into the control; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果用户可以向控件中输入提示字符，该值为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Even when <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AllowPromptAsInput%2A> is `true`, the prompt character must be valid for the current location in the mask in order to be accepted.
trans-unit.target: 即使<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AllowPromptAsInput%2A>是`true`，才能被接受的提示字符必须是有效的掩码中的当前位置。

trans-unit.source: For example, if <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PromptChar%2A> is "*", and the current location in the mask demands the user enter a digit, entering an asterisk (\*) will fail and cause the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected> event to occur.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PromptChar%2A>是"*"，并且当前掩码中的位置需要用户输入一个数字，输入一个星号 (\*) 将失败并且会导致<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected>事件发生。

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.IsOverwriteMode%2A> is `false`, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> will reject as invalid any character entry that would result in a violation anywhere in the mask.

trans-unit.source: Literals always occupy a static position in the mask at run time, and cannot be moved or deleted by the user.
trans-unit.target: 文本始终在运行时，占用掩码中的静态位置，无法移动或删除用户。

trans-unit.source: If you change a mask when <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> already contains user input filtered by a previous mask, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> will attempt to migrate that input into the new mask definition.
trans-unit.target: 如果更改掩码时<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>已包含用户输入筛选由以前的掩码，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>将尝试迁移到新的掩码定义该输入。

trans-unit.source: If it fails, it will clear the existing input.
trans-unit.target: 如果失败，则会清除现有输入。

trans-unit.source: Assigning a zero-length string as the mask will preserve any existing data in the control.
trans-unit.target: 将分配一个零长度字符串作为掩码将会保留控件中的任何现有数据。

trans-unit.source: When used with a zero-length mask, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> behaves like a single-line <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox> control.
trans-unit.target: 与零长度掩码一起使用时<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>的行为方式类似的单行<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>控件。

trans-unit.source: The decimal (.), thousandths (,), time (:), date (/), and currency ($) symbols default to displaying those symbols as defined by the application's culture.
trans-unit.target: 小数点 （.）、 分之几 （，）、 时间 （:）、 日期 （/），而货币 （$） 符号默认为由应用程序的区域性定义时，显示这些符号中。

trans-unit.source: You can force them to display symbols for another culture by using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.FormatProvider%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 你可以强制使用显示的另一个区域性符号<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.FormatProvider%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: Character insertion into the mask at run time is controlled by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.InsertKeyMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 在运行时的字符插入到掩码受<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.InsertKeyMode%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: Users can navigate through the mask by using the left and right arrow keys or the mouse cursor, and can skip optional positions in the mask by entering a space.
trans-unit.target: 用户可以通过使用左边距和右边的箭头键或鼠标光标浏览掩码，可以通过输入空格忽略掩码中的可选位置。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> supports all Unicode characters except for surrogates and vertically combined characters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> 支持除代理项的所有 Unicode 字符和垂直组合的字符。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether all required inputs have been entered into the input mask.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A> property defines the mask-parsing engine and the masking language used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A>属性都定义掩码分析引擎和使用的屏蔽语言<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>控件。

trans-unit.source: The default provider is the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MaskedTextProvider?displayProperty=nameWithType> class; however, a custom provider can be specified using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.%23ctor%28System.ComponentModel.MaskedTextProvider%29> constructor.
trans-unit.target: 默认的提供程序<xref:System.ComponentModel.MaskedTextProvider?displayProperty=nameWithType>类; 但是，自定义提供程序可以指定使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.%23ctor%28System.ComponentModel.MaskedTextProvider%29>构造函数。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A> cannot be set directly.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A> 不能直接设置。

trans-unit.source: However, setting some of the properties of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>—such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Mask%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AllowPromptAsInput%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.AsciiOnly%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Culture%2A>—may internally cause the creation of a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskedTextProvider%2A>.

trans-unit.target: 若要确定是否已输入仅必需的输入的元素，使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskCompleted%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected> is raised in the following situations:

trans-unit.source: An input character does not match the corresponding format element.

trans-unit.source: If the entire string only contains valid characters, according to their paste position in the input mask, then the entire operation will succeed.
trans-unit.target: 如果整个字符串只包含有效字符，根据在输入掩码中，其粘贴位置整个操作将会成功。

trans-unit.source: However, when a parsing error occurs, the behavior of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> depends on the value of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.RejectInputOnFirstFailure%2A>, as follows:

trans-unit.source: If this property is `true`, then processing of the input string stops at the invalid character.
trans-unit.target: 如果此属性为`true`，那么输入字符串的处理在无效的字符处停止。

trans-unit.target: 如果此属性为`false`，那么将拒绝的无效字符，但继续分析输入字符串中的下一个字符。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected> event is raised for every invalid character in the input string.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected>对输入字符串中每个无效字符引发事件。

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ResetOnPrompt%2A>，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ResetOnSpace%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SkipLiterals%2A>属性也会影响用户输入的解释。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines how an input character that matches the prompt character should be handled.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值确定应如何处理与提示字符匹配的输入字符。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the prompt character entered as input causes the current editable position in the mask to be reset; otherwise, <see langword="false" /> to indicate that the prompt character is to be processed as a normal input character.
trans-unit.target: 如果输入的提示字符会导致掩码中的当前可编辑位置被重置，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />，以指示要将提示字符作为正常输入字符进行处理。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> can treat two categories of characters—spaces and prompt characters—specially.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>可以将两种类别的字符-空格字符和提示字符-专门。

trans-unit.source: Typically, each input character will be tested against the mask and either accepted or rejected.

trans-unit.target: 当用户输入到掩码的提示字符时，它会导致要清除的当前掩码字符位置和当前位置，以推进到下一个可编辑的字符。

trans-unit.target: 提示字符被处理为标准的输入字符。

trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值确定应如何处理空白输入字符。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the space input character causes the current editable position in the mask to be reset; otherwise, <see langword="false" /> to indicate that it is to be processed as a normal input character.
trans-unit.target: 如果空白输入字符将导致重置掩码中的当前可编辑位置，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />，以指示要将其作为正常输入字符进行处理。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> can treat two categories of characters—spaces and prompt characters—specially.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>可以将两种类别的字符-空格字符和提示字符-专门。

trans-unit.source: Typically, each input character will be tested against the mask and either accepted or rejected.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，将对照掩码并测试每个输入的字符接受或拒绝。

trans-unit.source: Setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ResetOnSpace%2A> property to `true` will result in the current mask character position to be cleared and the current position to be advanced to the next editable character.
trans-unit.target: 设置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ResetOnSpace%2A>属性`true`将导致要清除的当前掩码字符位置和当前位置，以推进到下一个可编辑的字符。

trans-unit.source: The type of character input will determine whether the masking engine moves forward to the next character in the mask, or stays at the current position and waits for a matching character.
trans-unit.target: 字符输入的类型将确定是否屏蔽引擎将向前移动到掩码中的下一个字符或保留在当前位置并等待匹配的字符。

trans-unit.source: If the input character is a space, and does not match the current non-editable character in the mask, the masking engine will skip ahead to the next character in the mask.
trans-unit.target: 如果输入的字符是空格，并且与掩码中当前的非可编辑字符不匹配，屏蔽引擎将向前跳至掩码中的下一个字符。

trans-unit.source: If the input character is not a space, and does not match the current non-editable character in the mask, the masking engine will remain at the current mask position, and attempt to match the next input character against it.
trans-unit.target: 如果输入的字符不是一个空格，并且与掩码中当前的非可编辑字符不匹配，屏蔽引擎将保留在掩码当前位置，并尝试匹配对其下一步输入的字符。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" /> 类型的当前选定文本。

trans-unit.source: If no text is currently selected, this property resolves to an empty string.
trans-unit.target: 如果当前没有选定任何文本，此属性将解析为一个空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Selections retrieved using this property are formatted according to the control's formatting properties, such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Mask%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.FormatProvider%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 根据控件的格式设置属性，如格式化选择使用此属性检索<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Mask%2A>， <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.FormatProvider%2A>，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Selections set using this property behave like a Paste operation: each character is matched against the mask, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected> event is raised for invalid characters.
trans-unit.target: 选择使用此属性设置的行为类似于粘贴操作： 根据掩码，匹配每个字符和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected>个无效字符引发事件。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A> is `true`, literals and prompt characters are allowed when setting <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SelectedText%2A>, and will be removed silently unless they violate the mask.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A>是`true`，设置时允许原义字符和提示字符<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SelectedText%2A>，并且将以无提示方式删除，除非它们不与掩码冲突。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the user is allowed to reenter literal values.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示是否允许用户重新输入原义字符值。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to allow literals to be reentered; otherwise, <see langword="false" /> to prevent the user from overwriting literal characters.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 允许重新输入原义字符；否则 <see langword="false" /> 阻止用户覆盖原义字符。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: Input masks commonly contain literals.
trans-unit.target: 输入的掩码通常包含文本。

trans-unit.source: When the user enters characters into the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> at runtime, the current character position will sometimes fall on a literal.
trans-unit.target: 当用户输入到字符<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>在运行时，当前的字符位置将有时落在原义。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SkipLiterals%2A> property describes how user input for the next character is to be handled, as follows:
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SkipLiterals%2A>属性描述如何为下一个字符的用户输入处理的方式，，如下所示：

trans-unit.source: If this property is `true`, the user can either redundantly enter the same character as the literal at the current position, or can enter the next editable character, thereby jumping the current position to that position.
trans-unit.target: 如果此属性为`true`，用户可以不必要地输入相同的字符与该文本中的当前的位置，或者可以输入下一个可编辑的字符，从而从当前位置跳至该位置。

trans-unit.source: If this property is `false`, the user can only enter the next editable character.
trans-unit.target: 如果此属性为`false`，用户可以只需输入下一个可编辑的字符。

trans-unit.source: If the next position in the mask will not accept the literal character (for example, the user types "/" and the next position only accepts digits), the control will raise the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected> event.
trans-unit.target: 如果掩码中的下一个位置将不接受文本的字符 (例如，用户类型"/"和下一个位置仅接受数字)，则控件将引发<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.MaskInputRejected>事件。

trans-unit.source: As an example, in the "90/90/0000" date entry mask, the forward slash characters are literals.
trans-unit.target: 例如，在"90/90/0000"日期输入掩码中，正斜杠字符都是文本。

trans-unit.source: Assume that the user has entered two initial digits, "11", so the current position in the mask is at the first forward slash (/) literal.
trans-unit.target: 假定用户输入两个数字，"11"，掩码的当前位置位于第一个正斜杠 （/） 原义字符。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SkipLiterals%2A> is `true`, then the user has the following valid choices:
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.SkipLiterals%2A>是`true`，那么用户具有有效的以下选项：

trans-unit.source: The user can enter a "/" character.
trans-unit.target: 用户可以输入"/"字符。

trans-unit.source: This results in the position being moved to the next character, which in this example is the fourth position, a 9 masking element.
trans-unit.target: 这会导致正移至下一个字符，即在此示例中的第四个位置，9 屏蔽元素的位置。

trans-unit.source: The user can enter the next editable character, which in this example is a digit.
trans-unit.target: 用户可以输入下一个可编辑的字符，它在此示例是数字。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether literals and prompt characters are included in the formatted string.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值决定原义字符和提示字符是否包括在格式化字符串中。

trans-unit.source: One of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MaskFormat" /> values.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MaskFormat" /> 值之一。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.MaskFormat.IncludeLiterals" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Forms.MaskFormat.IncludeLiterals" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A> property determines how the literal and prompt characters in the mask are processed when the generating the formatted string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A>属性确定如何处理掩码中的文本，并提示字符时生成的格式化的字符串。

trans-unit.source: More specifically, it determines whether literal characters, prompt characters, or both are included in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 更具体地说，它决定原义字符和 / 或提示字符是否包括在<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: When prompt characters are excluded, they are transformed into spaces in the formatted string.
trans-unit.target: 如果提示字符被排除，它们将转换为格式字符串中的空格。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A> property serves a similar purpose with respect to how the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> property is interpreted.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.CutCopyMaskFormat%2A>属性有用途类似如何与<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>解释属性。

trans-unit.target: 用无效的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MaskFormat" /> 值设置的属性。

trans-unit.target: 返回表示当前掩码文本框的字符串。

trans-unit.target: 此方法重写 <see cref="M:System.Windows.Forms.TextBoxBase.ToString" />。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains information about the current <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.String" />，包含有关当前 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox" /> 的信息。

trans-unit.source: The string includes the type, a simplified view of the input string, and the formatted input string.
trans-unit.target: 该字符串包含类型、输入字符串的简化视图以及格式化后的输入字符串。

trans-unit.source: This version of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ToString%2A> method calls the base class implementation of this method, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBoxBase.ToString%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, then appends the input string after processing by the mask.
trans-unit.target: 此版本的<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ToString%2A>方法调用此方法的基类实现<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBoxBase.ToString%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>，然后在处理后追加的输入的字符串，由屏蔽。

trans-unit.source: This method honors properties that alter the appearance of the formatted string, with the following exceptions:
trans-unit.target: 此方法负责兑现 alter 格式的字符串，有以下例外的外观的属性：

trans-unit.source: The returned string always includes prompt and literal characters, regardless of the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 返回的字符串始终包括提示和文本的字符，而不考虑的值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TextMaskFormat%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: Password characters are ignored, so that the actual user-typed characters are returned.
trans-unit.target: 密码字符被忽略，以便将返回实际用户键入的字符。

trans-unit.source: In other words, the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PasswordChar%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A> properties are ignored.
trans-unit.target: 换而言之的值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PasswordChar%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A>属性会被忽略。

trans-unit.target: 当 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox" /> 已使用 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType" /> 属性完成了对当前值的分析时发生。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control will optionally validate user input against the type defined by its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>控件 （可选） 验证针对定义的类型的用户输入其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidatingType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性。

trans-unit.source: When this property is not `null`, the following series of events occurs:
trans-unit.target: 当此属性不是`null`，发生以下一系列事件：

trans-unit.source: The validation sequence begins when one of the following occurs:
trans-unit.target: 验证序列开始时以下项之一：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control looses focus.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> 控件失去焦点。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A> property is retrieved.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.Text%2A>检索属性。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidateText%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 调用 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.ValidateText%2A> 方法。

trans-unit.source: Any of these events result in a call to the `Parse` method of the type specified with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 任何这些事件导致调用`Parse`与指定的类型的方法<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.ValidatingType%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: `Parse` is responsible for the conversion of the formatted input string to the target type.
trans-unit.target: `Parse` 负责格式化的输入字符串转换为目标类型。

trans-unit.source: A successful conversion equates to a successful validation.
trans-unit.target: 成功转换相当于成功验证。

trans-unit.source: After `Parse` returns, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: 后`Parse`返回时，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>引发事件。

trans-unit.source: The event handler for this event is most commonly implemented to perform type or mask validation processing.
trans-unit.target: 此事件的事件处理程序最常实现来执行类型或蒙板验证处理。

trans-unit.source: It receives a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs> parameter containing information about the conversion; for example, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.IsValidInput%2A> member indicates whether the conversion was successful.
trans-unit.target: 它接收<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs>参数，其中包含信息有关的转换; 例如，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.IsValidInput%2A>成员指示转换是否成功。

trans-unit.source: After the event handler for the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event returns, the standard validation event, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating>, is raised.
trans-unit.target: 之后的事件处理程序<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>事件返回，该标准的验证事件， <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating>，将引发。

trans-unit.source: A handler can be implemented to perform standard validation, perhaps including canceling the event.
trans-unit.target: 可实现一个处理程序来执行标准的验证，可能包括取消事件。

trans-unit.source: If the event is not canceled in step 3, the standard control validation event <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validated> is raised.
trans-unit.target: 如果在步骤 3 中未取消事件，则标准控件的验证事件<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validated>引发。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property is set to `true` in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted> event handler, the event will be canceled and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control retains focus, unless the subsequent <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating> event sets its version of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property back to `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TypeValidationEventArgs.Cancel%2A>属性设置为`true`中<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.TypeValidationCompleted>事件处理程序，将取消事件与<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>控件将保留焦点，除非后续<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Validating>事件设置它的版本<xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性返回到`false`。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the operating system-supplied password character should be used.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示是否应使用操作系统提供的密码字符。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the system password should be used as the prompt character; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果应将系统密码用作提示字符，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A> property determines whether user-supplied input should be displayed in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> as multiple occurrences of a password character defined by the operating system.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A>属性确定用户提供的输入是否应显示在<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>作为密码字符由操作系统定义的多个匹配项。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A> functions similarly to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PasswordChar%2A> property, but instead of using a programmer-supplied character for the prompt, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A> uses a prompt defined by the operating system.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A> 功能类似于<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PasswordChar%2A>属性，而不是使用为提示，程序员提供的字符，但<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.UseSystemPasswordChar%2A>使用由操作系统定义的提示。

trans-unit.source: This property has precedence over <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PasswordChar%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此属性的优先级高于<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PasswordChar%2A>。

trans-unit.source: As a security consideration, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox> control disables cut and copy operations on password-protected strings.
trans-unit.target: 作为一种安全措施，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox>控件禁用对受密码保护的字符串的剪切和复制操作。

trans-unit.source: The password character specified is the same as the current prompt character, <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PromptChar" />.
trans-unit.target: 指定的密码字符与当前提示字符 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.MaskedTextBox.PromptChar" /> 相同。

trans-unit.source: The two are required to be different.
trans-unit.target: 这两者之间必须存在差异。

trans-unit.source: Converts the user input string to an instance of the validating type.
trans-unit.target: 将用户输入字符串转换为验证类型的一个实例。
